{
  "message": "feat(dashboard): add live metrics and log streaming to VM detail\n\nUpdate the VM detail template to use WebSocket connections for real-time\nupdates. The Resources panel now displays live CPU, memory, network, and\ndisk metrics with a \"Live\" indicator. The Logs panel streams logs in\nreal-time with pause, filter, and clear functionality.\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
